					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">So before I was considering using two sets of numbers for physics calculation on PAL and NTSC systems, but I now I'm searching for how to abuse DMC for a regular IRQ that would read the joypad into a circular buffer.<br /><br />I'm having difficulty understanding what to write in what registers. I know that I write $00 to $4010 and $40 to $4017 on reset, and that silent dpcm data is located at $c000, but that's about it. What's next?</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

