				<a name="p126289"></a>
				<b class="postauthor">rainwarrior</b>
			</td>
			<td width="100%" height="25">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p126289">Re: DMC IRQ for game logic?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=126289#p126289"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Mar 01, 2014 4:31 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
